    <item>
      <title>随着交易者避免长期债务，财政收益曲线会陡峭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/treasury-yield-curve-steepens-as-traders-avoid-long-term-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者要求赔偿关税会刺激美国通货膨胀的风险，因此长期的财政收益率在一个月内达到了最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/treasury-yield-curve-steepens-as-traders-avoid-long-term-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 13:46:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
